msgid ""
"box.cfg{audit_log = 'audit_tarantool.log'}\n"
"-- or\n"
"box.cfg{audit_log = 'file:audit_tarantool.log'}"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"This opens the ``audit_tarantool.log`` file for output in the server’s "
"default directory. If the ``audit_log`` string has no prefix or the prefix "
"``file:``, the string is interpreted as a file path."
