"where to send the message. The possible values are ``auth``, ``authpriv``, "
"``cron``, ``daemon``, ``ftp``, ``kern``, ``lpr``, ``mail``, ``news``, "
"``security``, ``syslog``, ``user``, ``uucp``, ``local0``, ``local1``, "
"``local2``, ``local3``, ``local4``, ``local5``, ``local6``, ``local7``. The "
"default value is ``local7``."
