msgid ""
"The ``syslog:server`` setting is the locator for the syslog server. It can "
"be a Unix socket path starting with \"unix:\" or an ipv4 port number. The "
"default socket value is ``/dev/log`` (on Linux) or ``/var/run/syslog`` (on "
"Mac OS). The default port value is 514, which is the UDP port."
